et har sn\u00f8dd s\u00e5 mye at det rekker \u00e5 sn\u00f8 igjen f\u00f8r vi er tilbake med br\u00f8ytebilen, sa ingeni\u00f8r Kjetil Haarberg ved Trondheim bydrift rundt klokken 10.30.", "Han forteller at i rushtiden m\u00e5 br\u00f8ytemannskapene prioritere hovedveien.", "- Det m\u00e5 vi, hvis ikke s\u00e5 blir det et fullstendig trafikkaos. Vi m\u00e5 s\u00f8rge for flyt i trafikken, forklarer Haarberg."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|trondheim"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "2ce256160187ceac9b69bbc59c8bfa1724bf779eb1b134a473b8bcacc3576ae4"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-01-11T15:37:37.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Renathe Skotvold m\u00e5tte trille barnevogna p\u00e5 veien da fortauet var nedsn\u00f8dd."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article9343805.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/kreativ+mor.JPG"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/2bc22a3669de8e300446bbb9322c2003a8c131cb.jpg?596f0494"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["- Hvis en bil hadde kj\u00f8rt i full fart, s\u00e5 hadde jeg ikke hatt noe \u00e5 stille opp med -adressa.no", "- Noen tutet p\u00e5 oss", "M\u00e5 hindre trafikkaos"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "2bc22a3669de8e300446bbb9322c2003a8c131cb"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "automotive"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["br\u00f8yte", "full fart", "bil", "skole", "vei", "sn\u00f8", "fortau"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["stabbursmoen", "heimdal", "emilie", "s\